e":"2019-02-14T08:17:24.000Z","msg":"以前係一面倒正評，宜家...<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ec9d6fc3da784a43ddcc8cbeee0cdf5ccec5bcd","tid":1021294,"uid":221265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"53054f6c916d07c6399f50fa8609465311e53a08","tid":1021294,"uid":9115,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T07:31:26.000Z","msg":"Post左咁撚多年都仲咁多新會然唔識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T08:19:55.000Z","msg":"睇錯新會<del>柑</del>"},{"pid":"a14c56eacf99efdc5bebe3fab22a9c31a1278084","tid":1021294,"uid":53441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T08:24:28.000Z","msg":"難分真與假"},{"pid":"cc6f9525e24ccbccafa1b1dc9044106ecd75544e","tid":1021294,"uid":7323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T08:29:02.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">ON99</span>"},{"pid":"84d0897170a649be1ae4bc1b6c9a92bc28d31895","tid":1021294,"uid":99700,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T08:31:43.000Z","msg":"呢篇野老過好多連登仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}